<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1027 saṁva <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> gaṁggagoṁḍacōḍavalanāṁṭi guddhavādināṁṭi peddaḍākarēmi śrī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>bhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku vyatiyipātanimittamuna cōḍamaṇḍalamuna tiruvi<unclear>ṁ</unclear>jalūrunāṁṭi gaṁjāṭṭapaṁca
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nadimuḍigoṇḍaṇḍaina vatsarāyuṇḍu beṭṭina Akhaṇḍavarttilōhadaṇḍudiviya 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīniki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyiṁcu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vārugā śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvara kilaramuna prōlabōla nāvayayuṁ peddibōla nāvayayu bādabōyu muniya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nayuṁ dalarāsi nāvayayu berasinavāru būṁṭagāṁ dalarāsi nāvaya Aḍapuna gusibōla nāvani vasamu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>na viḍcina InpaEḍlu 50 di nityapaḍi vōyaṁgala tribhuvanāṁkuśa <unclear>ma 1</unclear> ḍakarēmi likhitaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

